<HEADLINE>
<P>
PLANNING: REDOING THE SUNSET STRIP AREA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The exterior of the House of Blues on the Sunset Strip is an absolute affront 
to all civilized people. It is just one more example of the trashy taste of the 
West Hollywood Planning Commission and their City Council. 
</P>
<P>
 When one realizes that these same people are about to redo the Sunset Strip, 
permitting 14 high-rise buildings and adding 28,000 cars to the daily traffic, 
it gives new meaning to the words disgust and despair.  
</P>
<P>
 Just remember, when you vote, and do VOTE, that two candidates who approve of 
this Sunset Specific Plan, which will ultimately trap us in our homes and choke 
us to death, are running for the 42nd State Assembly seat. They are Abbe Land 
and Paul Koretz. 
</P>
<P>
 Dorothy Dorben 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles  
</P>
