<P>
 Helms Blocks Clinton Nominee: Sen. Jesse Helms (R-N.C.) is blocking the 
President's choice to head the Commodity Futures Trading Commission in 
retaliation for the transfer of a federal employee who criticized White House 
policy on gays and lesbians.Helms invoked a "hold" on the confirmation vote of 
