<DOCID> 060649 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 14, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 16; Column 1; Metro Desk 
